{"tid":632152,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日返工,畀鬼妹叫我返屋企","createTime":"2018-04-17T06:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T13:05:26.000Z","uid":37537,"like":12,"dislike":80,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e5b3bdaea37396c6c7113ee91e87615d89a64c94","tid":632152,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T06:17:59.000Z","msg":"我而家就係西人地方返工<br />\n<br />\n琴晚瞓得好差,今朝又要早起身<br />\n返工返到2 3點左右頂唔順就伏係枱抖下<br />\n<br />\n畀個鬼妹見到佢就問<br />\n<br />\nshe: Are you ok?<br />\nme: Yeah, I am just too tired.<br />\nshe: I am sorry. Can you go home?<br />\nme: I am ok. I just need to take a rest.<br />\nshe: But you can go home and take a nap. You can work at home. You can't be productive when you are tired.<br />\n<br />\n不過因為我有啲野一定要等到4 5點先做得,所以都係5點先走...<br />\n<br />\n經過呢件事,我覺得自己有奴性,當時有啲唔想2 3點返屋企<br />\n所以我今晚決定瞓夠哂聽日10-11點先返工"},{"pid":"2b1565b82e1c84dec0634f7423383658277fab55","tid":632152,"uid":20815,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T06:28:47.000Z","msg":"圖"},{"pid":"bd1b05a7bb07ddd33e13a7cb21379c175252ef72","tid":632152,"uid":52793,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T06:32:06.000Z","msg":"咩工嚟，請唔請人"},{"pid":"da072b22d435131b0ea2c8d4470c86f3b1e96925","tid":632152,"uid":37537,"like":11,"dislike":39,"score":-28,"quote":{"pid":"2b1565b82e1c84dec0634f7423383658277fab55","tid":632152,"uid":20815,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T06:28:47.000Z","msg":"圖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/145726_c4911a70666973f5be0c4b834fa13c13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F145726_c4911a70666973f5be0c4b834fa13c13.jpg&h=f873e149&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c914ea14381d8d62fd3a06191f928aef2db65df","tid":632152,"uid":33336,"like":63,"dislike":2,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:00:04.000Z","msg":"西人應該唔